<Abstract ID="Abs1" Language="En">
<Heading>Abstract</Heading>
<Para>As you saw in Chapter 2, Microsoft provides an identity selector in CardSpace as well as a Security Token Server (STS) for issuing personal cards. These are provided as part of the .NET Framework, and Microsoft has also enabled its web browser, Internet Explorer, and its services stack, Windows Communication Foundation, with mechanisms to interact with the identity selector.</Para>
